name: Cracking Dragon
desc: Cannot be destroyed by battle with a monster whose Level is lower than or equal to this card's. When your opponent Normal or Special Summons exactly 1 monster while this monster is on the field (except during the Damage Step): You can make that monster lose ATK equal to its Level x 200 (until the end of this turn), and if you do, inflict damage to your opponent equal to that lost ATK.
